"title='Release v1.7 - Pandemonium | Brute Ratel C4' description='Brute Ratel v1.7 [codename Pandemonium] is now available for download. This release is an entire overhaul of the Badger, Ratel Server and Commander to provide support for Yara evasions and Apple Silicon. Customers using v1.6 release should note that the Badger, Ratel server and Commander of v1.6 will not support v1.7. Do not upgrade to this release if you are in an active engagement. Operators should read this blog or the release notes section to understand the changes before upgrading. A quick summary of changes can be found in the release notes.' url='https://bruteratel.com/release/2023/07/27/Release-Pandemonium/' language='en' keywords=None robots='noindex, noindex, noindex' og_title='Release v1.7 - Pandemonium' og_description='Brute Ratel v1.7 [codename Pandemonium] is now available for download. This release is an entire overhaul of the Badger, Ratel Server and Commander to provide support for Yara evasions and Apple Silicon. Customers using v1.6 release should note that the Badger, Ratel server and Commander of v1.6 will not support v1.7. Do not upgrade to this release if you are in an active engagement. Operators should read this blog or the release notes section to understand the changes before upgrading. A quick summary of changes can be found in the release notes.' og_url='https://bruteratel.com/release/2023/07/27/Release-Pandemonium/' og_image='https://bruteratel.com/images/post_img/2023-07-27-Release-Pandemonium/badger.jpg' og_audio=None og_determiner=None og_locale='en_US' og_locale_alternate=None og_site_name='Brute Ratel C4' og_video=None favicon='https://bruteratel.com/images/brute_img/brute.png' dc_terms_created=None dc_date_created=None dc_date=None dc_terms_type=None dc_type=None dc_terms_audience=None dc_terms_subject=None dc_subject=None dc_description=None dc_terms_keywords=None modified_time=None published_time='2023-07-27T06:30:00+00:00' article_tag=None article_section=None so